file context/specs/20260714-024800_proposal-not-fork-reframing.md why: the authoritative reframing marker + the commit-rewrite exception
file context/specs/20260714-024800_warm-aura-date-atom-naming.md why: names the one stamp format (version/filename/folder) as the warm-aura date atom, TAME-guided
file expanding-prompts/20260714-024800_archiving-reviving-sweep-warm-aura-alignment.md why: the sweep as a naming-alignment pass with checkable claims
